For video quality I indeed give a thumbs up, but I also wish to give this movie itself a thumbs down, but I have to be a IMDB Pro paid member for that. Just like I always say: only the rich criticize and the poor just whine.

Okay, I try to review this. At first I thought, what a cheap movie name, but I still hoped it would be good. I was right and wrong.
The beginning was as I like to call it "something new". But, when I saw the first monster, I asked myself "Is this it?" and it kept getting worse. Indeed, from the first encounter to the end of the movie, it was nothing but cheap, poorly made, illogical shit.
The beginning had a good story, but the rest had no story, more like just an "idea", but sb just forgot to turn that idea into a proper story.

I bet this movie will eventually have score of 3 at IMDB. I already see the chart taking a nice fall.

This is actually the second "available (at TPB) before public release" movie that sucked. Must be a marketing trick or smthn.

Never download any movies, which don't have any ratings or pro. reviews. Early availability is no excuse.
